WEBVTT

01:25.910 --> 01:35.000
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.420 --> 01:37.940
[Episode 30]

01:38.479 --> 01:40.610
You're interested in paintings, huh?

01:48.229 --> 01:50.030
Where did you get this painting?

01:50.140 --> 01:51.070
I just bought it.

01:51.430 --> 01:52.890
Then, Miss Luo, do you know

01:53.140 --> 01:55.070
who the artist of this painting is?

01:55.370 --> 01:56.310
I don't know.

01:57.420 --> 01:58.560
But I do know that

01:58.560 --> 01:59.729
with the brushstrokes

01:59.729 --> 02:01.190
and feel of this painting,

02:01.500 --> 02:03.340
it's bound to be priceless.

02:04.930 --> 02:06.830
An artist of exceptional talent

02:06.950 --> 02:08.949
will not stay in obscurity forever.

02:09.620 --> 02:11.430
A true friend is never far away...

02:11.430 --> 02:12.690
-What?
-Master Cao...

02:13.020 --> 02:14.150
We should get going.

02:16.590 --> 02:17.920
I won't see you out then.

02:19.090 --> 02:19.690
Goodbye.

02:26.960 --> 02:27.710
Miss Luo.

02:29.120 --> 02:29.870
What I'm about to say

02:29.870 --> 02:31.460
might be a little presumptuous.

02:31.460 --> 02:33.090
From the look of your complexion,

02:33.090 --> 02:34.960
I think you might have

02:34.960 --> 02:35.780
a minor health issue.

02:35.780 --> 02:37.910
I'll help you nurse it if you have time.

02:38.300 --> 02:39.400
Am I sick?

02:39.530 --> 02:40.260
Don't worry,

02:40.710 --> 02:42.310
I can help you take care of it.

02:43.970 --> 02:45.700
Then I won't stand on ceremony.

02:46.240 --> 02:47.840
I'll go see you when I'm free.

02:49.470 --> 02:50.560
I'd recommend sooner rather than later.

02:50.560 --> 02:52.750
Nursing health issues
shouldn't be delayed.

02:52.750 --> 02:54.150
Here is my business card.

02:55.690 --> 02:56.970
[Cao Ye, Chairman]

03:00.520 --> 03:02.910
Master Cao, this way.

03:14.190 --> 03:15.240
Thank you, Ranran.

03:15.240 --> 03:16.570
Thanks so much, Ranran.

03:16.840 --> 03:17.860
Don't mention it.

03:17.860 --> 03:19.120
That's because your restaurant

03:19.120 --> 03:20.380
makes delicious food.

03:20.800 --> 03:21.240
You flatter us.

03:21.240 --> 03:22.000
I'll get back to work then.

03:22.000 --> 03:22.740
Keep in touch.

03:22.740 --> 03:23.430
Keep in touch.

03:23.430 --> 03:25.230
Let me know if you need anything.

03:30.750 --> 03:31.440
Liang.

03:31.890 --> 03:32.310
Liang.

03:32.310 --> 03:33.260
Come out and help. Hurry.

03:33.260 --> 03:34.400
-It's so busy out here.
-I’m coming.

03:34.400 --> 03:35.020
Can't you read the room?

03:35.020 --> 03:35.680
Here you go.

03:35.790 --> 03:36.190
Okay.

03:36.190 --> 03:37.060
Thank you.

03:37.840 --> 03:38.500
Hurry up!

03:38.520 --> 03:39.350
Coming.

03:39.960 --> 03:40.960
Easy, easy.

03:53.480 --> 03:55.010
Okay, I'll get that for you.

04:00.030 --> 04:00.800
Bonjour.

04:02.580 --> 04:03.980
What are you doing here?

04:04.090 --> 04:05.870
I didn't want you to work hard alone.

04:05.870 --> 04:06.960
Tao, hurry up.

04:07.000 --> 04:08.330
The guests are waiting.

04:08.370 --> 04:08.930
Coming.

04:10.650 --> 04:11.360
Here, here.

04:13.070 --> 04:13.930
Chili, please.

04:14.010 --> 04:15.140
Let me get it for you.

04:16.209 --> 04:17.070
-Kitchen, be quick.
-Okay.

04:17.070 --> 04:18.670
We have a lot of guests today.

04:26.630 --> 04:27.570
Thank you.

04:27.600 --> 04:28.260
Here you go.

04:28.500 --> 04:29.430
Enjoy your meal.

04:29.980 --> 04:31.430
No more dishes to serve.
I'll get back to washing.

04:31.430 --> 04:32.290
Okay.

04:34.370 --> 04:35.230
How is the food?

04:35.250 --> 04:36.060
Pretty good.

04:36.130 --> 04:37.240
Then let's

04:37.240 --> 04:38.159
meet at 1:00 p.m.

04:38.159 --> 04:39.930
at the restaurant entrance on time.

04:39.930 --> 04:41.060
I'll go pay the bill.

04:43.760 --> 04:45.480
These 3 tables are all our clients.

04:45.480 --> 04:46.890
Calculate them together
and give us a discount.

04:46.890 --> 04:47.870
Yes, I've been told to do so.

04:47.870 --> 04:48.580
Thank you.

05:34.370 --> 05:36.820
Time to eat, Boss Xu.

05:37.890 --> 05:38.560
Hurry up.

05:40.740 --> 05:41.570
Mr. Jia's distribution for us in Russia

05:41.570 --> 05:43.040
this time

05:43.070 --> 05:44.130
was a huge success.

05:44.190 --> 05:45.700
Shouldn't we celebrate?

05:45.860 --> 05:47.100
Of course we should.

05:48.500 --> 05:49.180
Come on.

05:49.680 --> 05:50.250
Come on.

05:50.570 --> 05:51.180
Cheers.

05:51.510 --> 05:52.940
First battle won.

05:53.130 --> 05:54.000
Keep up the momentum!

05:54.000 --> 05:55.200
Keep up the momentum!

06:00.360 --> 06:00.690
Let's eat.

06:00.690 --> 06:01.130
Wait.

06:01.500 --> 06:02.310
Before we eat,

06:02.330 --> 06:03.920
could you sign the contract,

06:03.920 --> 06:04.860
Boss Zhuang,

06:04.890 --> 06:06.310
and a few remittance forms?

06:06.310 --> 06:07.400
Let's eat first.

06:07.620 --> 06:08.750
Just sign them first, please.

06:08.750 --> 06:10.180
Then we can eat in peace.

06:10.300 --> 06:11.030
Here you are.

06:13.690 --> 06:15.420
I spent all afternoon cooking.

06:17.900 --> 06:19.050
[Remittance Advice]

06:22.490 --> 06:24.390
[Remittance Advice]

06:24.480 --> 06:26.360
[Purchase Contract]

06:25.770 --> 06:27.040
Why are there so many?

06:26.540 --> 06:29.130
[Property Purchase Contract]

06:30.170 --> 06:31.830
Property Purchase Contract?

06:34.080 --> 06:34.940
[Contract] [Party A: Xu Yang]
[Party B: Zhuang Zhuang]

06:35.159 --> 06:36.600
You bought this place?

06:36.620 --> 06:37.950
Just one last step,

06:38.350 --> 06:41.170
which is the owner's signature.

06:42.070 --> 06:42.690
Come on.

06:43.480 --> 06:44.340
The final page.

06:46.680 --> 06:47.280
Sign here.

06:52.740 --> 06:53.370
But...

06:54.010 --> 06:55.480
why is only my name on it?

06:54.200 --> 06:54.990
[Property Purchase Contract]

06:55.110 --> 06:56.350
[Contract] [Party A: Xu Yang]
[Party B: Zhuang Zhuang]

06:57.770 --> 06:58.860
I was worried

06:58.890 --> 06:59.900
if we argue later

06:59.930 --> 07:00.450
and you kick me out,

07:00.450 --> 07:01.580
I'd talk back to you.

07:02.370 --> 07:03.220
If my name wasn't on it,

07:03.220 --> 07:04.240
you'd dare talk back?

07:04.240 --> 07:05.170
I wouldn't dare.

07:06.000 --> 07:07.260
Alright, just sign it.

07:09.470 --> 07:11.150
[Party B: Signature: Zhuang Zhuang]

07:16.040 --> 07:16.680
We finally

07:16.680 --> 07:18.040
have our own home.

07:20.360 --> 07:22.660
We finally have a home in Beijing.

07:35.120 --> 07:35.750
Hello.

07:36.420 --> 07:37.120
Sophia.

07:37.810 --> 07:38.810
How have you been?

07:39.510 --> 07:40.620
Everything is great.

07:40.620 --> 07:41.680
Zhuang Zhuang mentioned you

07:41.680 --> 07:42.580
to me yesterday.

07:42.580 --> 07:43.710
You two should chat.

07:43.980 --> 07:45.680
Okay, I miss her too.

07:45.680 --> 07:46.330
Sophia.

07:46.890 --> 07:48.050
Hello, Sophia.

07:48.300 --> 07:49.760
How's your health lately?

07:50.070 --> 07:50.800
Pretty good.

07:50.950 --> 07:52.810
I really miss you, Zhuang Zhuang.

07:54.370 --> 07:56.230
Did you receive the down jackets?

07:56.240 --> 07:57.100
Yes, I did.

07:57.390 --> 07:59.370
They look very warm.

07:59.830 --> 08:01.690
They will definitely be popular.

08:02.560 --> 08:03.660
That's good.

08:04.000 --> 08:04.540
However,

08:04.930 --> 08:06.740
I know making this compromise

08:06.740 --> 08:07.870
must be hard for you.

08:08.060 --> 08:08.860
But it's okay.

08:09.010 --> 08:10.610
Everything has a beginning.

08:10.660 --> 08:11.590
What do you mean?

08:12.450 --> 08:13.700
All your down jackets

08:13.810 --> 08:15.620
are labeled "Made in Italy."

08:15.980 --> 08:17.390
Didn't you know it?

08:20.220 --> 08:21.800
I'm not really clear on the details.

08:21.800 --> 08:22.970
I'll ask Shengli.

08:23.630 --> 08:24.130
Okay.

08:24.680 --> 08:25.240
Alright.

08:25.510 --> 08:27.370
Take good care of yourself.

08:28.250 --> 08:29.010
You too.

08:29.600 --> 08:30.540
Okay, bye.

08:31.930 --> 08:32.730
What's wrong?

08:34.440 --> 08:35.600
Mr. Jia relabeled

08:35.600 --> 08:36.330
our clothes.

08:37.030 --> 08:38.159
That's impossible.

08:38.409 --> 08:40.080
It's clearly stated in the contract.

08:40.080 --> 08:42.000
Sophia said the clothes she received

08:42.000 --> 08:43.860
were all labeled "Made in Italy."

08:52.510 --> 08:53.370
Hello, Mr. Jia.

08:53.820 --> 08:54.390
Didn't we

08:54.410 --> 08:55.740
make it clear back then?

08:56.000 --> 08:58.250
It's also clearly stated in the contract.

08:58.250 --> 08:58.840
Why on earth

08:58.840 --> 08:59.630
have you put "Made in Italy"

08:59.630 --> 09:00.680
on our clothes?

09:01.290 --> 09:02.600
The goods are in my hands.

09:02.600 --> 09:03.910
I can sell them however I want.

09:03.910 --> 09:04.920
That's fraud!

09:05.150 --> 09:06.750
This is a breach of contract.

09:07.500 --> 09:09.050
If I sell them with Chinese labels,

09:09.050 --> 09:10.390
nobody will buy them.

09:10.720 --> 09:12.200
I paid you

09:12.200 --> 09:13.500
for the goods.

09:13.620 --> 09:14.150
I can't just let my inventory

09:14.150 --> 09:15.350
go to waste, can I?

09:15.480 --> 09:17.410
Who's going to compensate for my loss?

09:17.410 --> 09:18.740
No matter what it takes,

09:18.890 --> 09:19.510
putting the money

09:19.510 --> 09:20.910
in your own pocket first,

09:20.960 --> 09:22.650
that's the way of doing business.

09:22.650 --> 09:24.310
What you're doing is illegal.

09:24.630 --> 09:25.560
I'm telling you,

09:25.870 --> 09:27.930
we are terminating our cooperation.

09:31.650 --> 09:32.980
It was all written in the contract,

09:32.980 --> 09:34.050
clearly stated.

09:34.050 --> 09:35.110
How dare he do this?

09:36.030 --> 09:37.510
He really stoops so low.

09:38.030 --> 09:39.630
It's harder than we imagined

09:39.740 --> 09:41.220
to stick to our own brand.

09:41.910 --> 09:43.920
This next batch of clothes

09:43.940 --> 09:45.570
is about to leave the factory.

09:45.570 --> 09:46.900
We can only look for some

09:46.910 --> 09:48.550
small-scale independent retailers.

09:48.550 --> 09:50.130
We can definitely sell them.

09:50.130 --> 09:51.790
Our clothes are of good quality.

09:51.790 --> 09:52.920
But the cycle

09:53.080 --> 09:54.140
will be prolonged.

09:54.530 --> 09:55.130
And we're about to

09:55.130 --> 09:56.750
pay the factory workers' wages.

09:56.750 --> 09:57.290
There's also

09:57.290 --> 09:59.350
the raw material cost they advanced.

09:59.410 --> 10:01.140
I learned this before at Ruhua.

10:02.150 --> 10:04.610
A signature can double the value
of a design.

10:05.720 --> 10:06.930
A brand logo

10:07.290 --> 10:09.220
can determine the value of an item.

10:09.650 --> 10:10.600
But if we

10:10.630 --> 10:12.440
don't stick with building our brand,

10:12.440 --> 10:13.540
all our efforts

10:13.740 --> 10:15.360
will just end up a one-off deal.

10:15.360 --> 10:16.290
How about this?

10:17.840 --> 10:19.520
Let's transfer some profit

10:19.630 --> 10:21.230
from the shoe factory first.

10:21.360 --> 10:22.630
We can't owe wages.

10:24.360 --> 10:25.890
This afternoon, I'll contact

10:25.890 --> 10:28.050
the shoe distributors and
market representatives

10:28.050 --> 10:29.450
we've been working with.

10:29.510 --> 10:31.370
See if they can help find a way out.

10:31.620 --> 10:32.600
We know these people

10:32.600 --> 10:33.860
pretty well.

10:34.570 --> 10:35.220
They're also

10:35.220 --> 10:36.850
sincerely wanting Chinese goods

10:36.850 --> 10:38.300
to make a name overseas.

10:38.560 --> 10:41.020
Let's help each other out
at a time like this.

10:41.360 --> 10:41.910
Alright.

10:42.240 --> 10:43.600
Let's not think about it for now.

10:43.600 --> 10:44.530
Let's eat first.

10:54.340 --> 10:55.910
Doesn't Zongbao always say

10:56.410 --> 10:58.830
"every obstacle can be overcome"?

11:01.240 --> 11:02.030
You have me.

11:13.440 --> 11:14.970
Bro, you're back.

11:15.190 --> 11:16.360
Perfect timing. I'm going out for a bit.

11:16.360 --> 11:17.490
Where are you going?

11:17.530 --> 11:18.550
I'm going to the basement storage.

11:18.550 --> 11:19.510
There will be customers

11:19.510 --> 11:20.240
coming to pick up goods tomorrow.

11:20.240 --> 11:21.580
I'll go and register for an appointment.

11:21.580 --> 11:22.980
What's in this envelope?

11:25.030 --> 11:25.720
This...

11:26.360 --> 11:27.130
The registration form.

11:27.130 --> 11:28.310
But we need two copies, right?

11:28.310 --> 11:30.080
Otherwise, security won't have a backup.

11:30.080 --> 11:31.100
I remember

11:31.790 --> 11:33.850
we registered yesterday, didn't we?

11:34.580 --> 11:36.150
Yes, we did,

11:36.170 --> 11:37.030
but we also need to give one copy

11:37.030 --> 11:38.250
to security.

11:38.320 --> 11:38.970
Otherwise, tomorrow morning,

11:38.970 --> 11:40.060
he won't let us in.

11:40.290 --> 11:41.270
Okay, go ahead.

11:41.460 --> 11:42.120
Okay.

11:43.170 --> 11:44.030
By the way, bro,

11:44.750 --> 11:46.810
the suppliers have all contacted us.

11:46.820 --> 11:48.360
The sales reps for leather shoes

11:48.360 --> 11:49.970
were really a big help this time.

11:49.970 --> 11:50.530
Our goods

11:50.530 --> 11:51.720
are famous in Russia.

11:51.720 --> 11:51.980
Everyone knows

11:51.980 --> 11:53.510
we're a good Chinese brand.

11:54.290 --> 11:55.750
But can the factory

11:55.770 --> 11:57.170
keep up with production?

11:57.550 --> 11:58.220
The latest batch

11:58.220 --> 12:00.480
won't be ready until the end of December.

12:01.010 --> 12:02.580
It's fine, I'll talk to them.

12:02.580 --> 12:04.440
Good things are worth waiting for.

12:04.440 --> 12:05.030
Bro, Sis,

12:05.340 --> 12:05.960
thanks to your decision

12:05.960 --> 12:07.160
to persist back then,

12:07.480 --> 12:08.200
we really made it

12:08.200 --> 12:09.970
through this crisis.

12:10.620 --> 12:11.240
I'll get back to work.

12:11.240 --> 12:12.100
Okay, go ahead.

12:12.580 --> 12:14.040
Thanks for your hard work.

12:16.520 --> 12:18.720
Running around all day, you must be tired.

12:18.720 --> 12:19.320
Not at all.

12:19.770 --> 12:20.530
Not at all?

12:21.600 --> 12:22.670
Shipping the goods out

12:22.670 --> 12:23.910
will be a relief.

12:25.370 --> 12:26.910
Now that we've hired more workers,

12:26.910 --> 12:28.510
the volume has gone right up.

12:28.550 --> 12:30.220
Yes, volume goes up,

12:30.270 --> 12:32.150
but we can't let quality slip.

12:32.860 --> 12:33.290
I think

12:33.290 --> 12:35.950
we should visit the factory
before the New Year.

12:35.980 --> 12:37.990
To hand out some New Year gifts,

12:38.080 --> 12:39.790
and most importantly,

12:39.870 --> 12:41.240
to make sure overtime pay is settled.

12:41.240 --> 12:42.150
That'll keep everyone

12:42.150 --> 12:43.800
motivated to work hard.

12:44.320 --> 12:45.180
Sure.

12:45.510 --> 12:46.100
Then tomorrow,

12:46.100 --> 12:47.560
I'll go shopping with you.

12:47.700 --> 12:48.360
Okay.

12:53.620 --> 12:55.940
Mr. Chen, here is what you asked for.

12:59.940 --> 13:00.790
For their down jackets,

13:00.790 --> 13:02.890
the raw materials and craftsmanship used

13:02.890 --> 13:04.090
are all written on it.

13:04.170 --> 13:04.770
However, for some

13:04.770 --> 13:06.210
specially customized items,

13:06.210 --> 13:06.770
you'll need to contact

13:06.770 --> 13:07.860
their suppliers.

13:08.530 --> 13:10.310
I've also prepared the supplier list.

13:10.310 --> 13:11.320
It's at the back.

13:14.430 --> 13:15.330
Good job.

13:29.180 --> 13:30.840
All right, this is far enough.

13:31.080 --> 13:32.710
Thanks everyone for your hard work.

13:32.710 --> 13:33.370
We still need to

13:33.370 --> 13:34.740
ensure safe production.

13:34.740 --> 13:35.220
If you have any questions,

13:35.220 --> 13:36.340
feel free to contact us anytime.

13:36.340 --> 13:37.470
Look at you two.

13:37.500 --> 13:39.220
You're so busy with sales
before the New Year,

13:39.220 --> 13:40.180
yet you made a special trip

13:40.180 --> 13:41.060
to see us.

13:41.210 --> 13:42.810
All right, don't mention it.

13:43.050 --> 13:44.510
We only exist because of the factory.

13:44.510 --> 13:46.840
The factory is the foundation
of everything we have.

13:46.840 --> 13:47.940
The cafeteria has food ready.

13:47.940 --> 13:48.480
Grab a quick bite

13:48.480 --> 13:49.510
It won't take much time.

13:49.510 --> 13:50.630
We really appreciate it,

13:50.630 --> 13:51.340
but the two of us

13:51.340 --> 13:52.690
still have to go to 2 other factories.

13:52.690 --> 13:53.910
We have to hurry on the way.

13:53.910 --> 13:55.620
All right, I won't keep you then.

13:55.620 --> 13:56.340
Drive safely.

13:56.340 --> 13:57.270
Have a safe trip.

13:57.590 --> 13:59.120
Leave the production to us.

13:59.530 --> 14:00.470
Rest assured.

14:00.530 --> 14:00.770
Okay.

14:00.770 --> 14:01.320
We will.

14:01.690 --> 14:03.150
Happy New Year in advance.

14:03.740 --> 14:04.340
Happy New Year.

14:04.340 --> 14:05.200
Happy New Year.

14:05.910 --> 14:07.200
Okay, I won't see you out.

14:07.200 --> 14:07.760
I'll leave you to it.

14:07.760 --> 14:08.260
Bye.

14:08.290 --> 14:09.410
-Bye.
-Thanks for your hard work.

14:09.410 --> 14:09.960
Bye.

14:13.210 --> 14:14.650
Should we finish it

14:14.670 --> 14:16.330
all at once these 2 days, or...

14:16.370 --> 14:17.000
Since we're already out here,

14:17.000 --> 14:18.400
let's finish it in one go.

14:18.630 --> 14:20.490
I'm just afraid you'll get tired.

14:20.630 --> 14:21.750
Everyone is working so hard.

14:21.750 --> 14:23.680
We have nothing to complain about.

14:24.170 --> 14:25.200
Okay. When we go back this time,

14:25.200 --> 14:27.000
let's do the accounts properly.

14:27.100 --> 14:27.900
This time,

14:27.920 --> 14:28.980
because we need to rush
this batch of goods,

14:28.980 --> 14:29.960
we hired a lot of extra workers.

14:29.960 --> 14:31.220
But the efficiency

14:31.330 --> 14:32.990
has improved significantly.

14:34.100 --> 14:35.140
After this trip,

14:35.160 --> 14:36.270
let's not go back to Beijing.

14:36.270 --> 14:37.570
Let's go back to our hometowns.

14:37.570 --> 14:38.930
We have to deliver the goods
after the New Year.

14:38.930 --> 14:39.970
Let's not go back this year.

14:39.970 --> 14:41.430
Two days won't make a difference.

14:41.430 --> 14:42.600
Everyone is busy with production.

14:42.600 --> 14:44.330
It's no use for us to just worry.

14:45.510 --> 14:46.930
We'll stay for 2 days,

14:47.080 --> 14:47.820
just 2 days.

14:48.500 --> 14:49.190
Okay.

14:49.350 --> 14:51.090
Then we'll go back to Wenzhou first,

14:51.090 --> 14:52.150
and then back to...

14:52.900 --> 14:53.990
-Yantai.
-Yantai.

15:02.460 --> 15:03.450
Look at you.

15:03.480 --> 15:04.250
You bring so many things

15:04.250 --> 15:05.370
every time you come back.

15:05.370 --> 15:06.410
Let Shengli take care of them.

15:06.410 --> 15:07.030
Come over here.

15:07.030 --> 15:07.920
Sweetheart,

15:07.940 --> 15:08.760
Zhuang Zhuang,

15:08.760 --> 15:09.530
sit here and rest.

15:09.530 --> 15:10.790
Come, have some water.

15:10.850 --> 15:11.910
Thank you, Auntie.

15:12.070 --> 15:12.640
Auntie,

15:13.340 --> 15:15.320
these are clothes my mom made

15:15.340 --> 15:16.340
for you and Uncle.

15:16.490 --> 15:17.620
See if you like them.

15:17.700 --> 15:19.750
A new piece of clothing every year.

15:19.750 --> 15:20.550
Thank your mom.

15:20.550 --> 15:22.600
-She makes one for me every year.
-You're welcome. It's no trouble.

15:22.600 --> 15:23.600
I tried it just now.

15:23.600 --> 15:25.600
-It fits perfectly.
-Do you like it?

15:25.620 --> 15:26.600
Say hello to your parents.

15:26.600 --> 15:27.390
I did.

15:27.530 --> 15:28.990
They said hello to you too.

15:29.790 --> 15:31.650
-Thank them.
-The dishes are almost ready.

15:31.650 --> 15:33.110
Shall we start the dinner?

15:33.410 --> 15:33.910
Yes.

15:34.340 --> 15:35.200
By the way, Zhuang Zhuang.

15:35.200 --> 15:36.070
You know what?

15:36.100 --> 15:37.420
Do you smell that?

15:37.440 --> 15:39.120
Your uncle remembers that
you loved the flatfish

15:39.120 --> 15:40.480
last time you were here.

15:40.530 --> 15:41.980
He's already stewing it for you.

15:41.980 --> 15:43.000
Smells so good.

15:43.030 --> 15:43.740
Whatever you want to eat
these couple of days,

15:43.740 --> 15:44.990
just tell him.

15:45.120 --> 15:45.500
Okay.

15:45.530 --> 15:46.280
Let him make it for you.

15:46.280 --> 15:47.440
-Nourish yourself.
-Yeah, I’ll cook for you.

15:47.440 --> 15:49.500
Then I'll just have my usual 3 dishes.

15:49.910 --> 15:51.680
-You?
-What does it have to do with you?

15:51.680 --> 15:52.250
Exactly.

15:52.250 --> 15:53.440
We're talking about
what Zhuang Zhuang likes to eat,

15:53.440 --> 15:54.000
okay?

15:54.240 --> 15:54.940
Okay.

15:54.960 --> 15:56.310
Thank you, Uncle and Auntie.

15:56.310 --> 15:57.650
Go check on your fish.

15:57.670 --> 15:58.730
Don't let it burn.

15:58.770 --> 15:59.220
Yes, yes.

15:59.220 --> 15:59.630
Go, go.

15:59.670 --> 16:00.430
Hurry up.

16:00.500 --> 16:01.460
Hurry.

16:01.510 --> 16:02.550
Okay.

16:06.030 --> 16:07.220
Zhuang Zhuang,

16:08.270 --> 16:09.100
when you two came back this time,

16:09.100 --> 16:11.350
I noticed you both look a bit thinner.

16:11.700 --> 16:13.410
Did you not eat well in Beijing?

16:13.410 --> 16:15.250
Did you not take good care of yourselves?

16:15.250 --> 16:17.000
We were a bit busy lately.

16:17.790 --> 16:19.650
We'll definitely eat well later.

16:19.980 --> 16:22.370
Yes, take good care of yourselves.

16:22.860 --> 16:24.770
Shengli, how's the garlic?

16:24.870 --> 16:25.940
-Hurry up.
-Done.

16:26.460 --> 16:27.650
Haven't you mashed it yet?  Hurry.

16:27.650 --> 16:28.600
I'm so happy

16:28.630 --> 16:30.180
you're back.

16:30.600 --> 16:31.360
Look at your uncle.

16:31.360 --> 16:32.720
He's also thrilled.

16:33.120 --> 16:34.980
We'll come back often in the future.

16:34.980 --> 16:36.000
Definitely.

16:39.130 --> 16:40.240
Honey.

16:40.260 --> 16:41.360
Coming.

16:41.940 --> 16:42.460
Didn't you say

16:42.460 --> 16:44.320
you wanted to eat more cucumber shreds?

16:44.320 --> 16:45.580
I cut some more for you.

16:45.630 --> 16:46.360
Here you are.

16:47.130 --> 16:48.080
Have a try.

16:48.320 --> 16:49.100
Let me try.

16:51.620 --> 16:53.170
Eat slowly, don't choke.

16:54.290 --> 16:55.580
I was so mad today.

16:55.580 --> 16:56.620
I need to eat more.

16:56.740 --> 16:57.340
Why so mad?

16:57.340 --> 16:58.580
Who made you angry?

16:59.370 --> 17:00.830
There was a tourist today.

17:01.360 --> 17:03.240
He said I made the schedule too tight,

17:03.240 --> 17:05.270
and it was so tiring that
he couldn't sleep.

17:05.270 --> 17:07.000
He wanted me to cut out some scenic spots.

17:07.000 --> 17:07.640
I said,

17:08.660 --> 17:09.790
this is a group tour;

17:09.810 --> 17:11.609
it's not just for one person.

17:12.069 --> 17:13.400
-Yeah.
-Before I could finish,

17:13.400 --> 17:14.930
he started arguing with me.

17:16.660 --> 17:17.450
I said, fine,

17:17.960 --> 17:19.700
let's have a meeting together.

17:19.980 --> 17:21.280
If everyone agrees,

17:21.300 --> 17:22.810
I will discuss it with the company.

17:22.810 --> 17:24.000
Guess what he said?

17:24.770 --> 17:26.030
"Don't discuss it with me.

17:26.030 --> 17:28.000
I pay, so you just listen to me."

17:28.160 --> 17:28.870
Right?

17:29.110 --> 17:30.350
He was just that bossy.

17:30.350 --> 17:31.720
You acted exactly like him.

17:31.720 --> 17:33.160
I could just guess.

17:33.220 --> 17:35.220
Rich people are all bossy like that.

17:35.680 --> 17:36.980
When I get rich,

17:38.220 --> 17:39.570
I'll let you be that bossy too.

17:39.570 --> 17:40.920
Next time you meet someone like this,

17:40.920 --> 17:41.790
just tell him,

17:42.270 --> 17:43.460
"If you don't have money,

17:43.460 --> 17:44.630
join a group tour

17:44.960 --> 17:45.940
and listen to the guide.

17:45.940 --> 17:48.070
If you have money, get a private tour."

17:49.310 --> 17:50.910
Let him do whatever he wants.

17:52.050 --> 17:53.050
Are you happy now?

17:55.560 --> 17:56.790
Still a little angry.

17:57.400 --> 17:57.830
Well...

17:57.830 --> 17:59.760
How about you cheer me up a bit more?

17:59.940 --> 18:00.180
What?

18:00.180 --> 18:00.680
You want me to

18:00.680 --> 18:01.920
put on a performance?

18:02.010 --> 18:02.890
That'll be nice.

18:02.890 --> 18:04.880
You reacted quite fast.

18:05.310 --> 18:06.330
It's the middle of the night.

18:06.330 --> 18:07.300
I can't play the sax

18:07.300 --> 18:08.540
or the guitar.

18:09.660 --> 18:10.120
How about

18:10.120 --> 18:11.350
I do a kip-up for you?

18:11.400 --> 18:12.160
Sure.

18:13.180 --> 18:14.070
I want to see.

18:14.420 --> 18:15.480
Come on.

18:15.550 --> 18:17.420
Just show me.

18:19.990 --> 18:20.680
Alright.

18:21.220 --> 18:22.480
Sit on the windowsill.

18:22.640 --> 18:23.200
Okay.

18:23.200 --> 18:25.060
Eat while you watch.

18:29.220 --> 18:30.480
Here comes the kip-up.

18:40.160 --> 18:40.740
Hurry up.

18:49.300 --> 18:50.480
I'm gathering my energy.

18:50.480 --> 18:51.430
Wait a moment.

18:51.550 --> 18:52.550
Watch carefully.

19:01.530 --> 19:02.310
How was it?

19:02.500 --> 19:03.140
Awesome.

19:04.070 --> 19:05.830
I swear, a Beijing boy

19:05.960 --> 19:07.110
can't handle compliments.

19:07.110 --> 19:08.140
Once you praise me...

19:08.140 --> 19:09.530
Do another one.

19:09.700 --> 19:10.530
Another one?

19:11.000 --> 19:12.170
Okay, another one.

19:12.940 --> 19:14.130
Another one.

19:14.770 --> 19:15.680
Another one.

19:18.270 --> 19:20.090
Kip-up plus a forward roll.

19:20.160 --> 19:20.750
Great!

19:25.750 --> 19:26.680
Are you alright?

19:27.720 --> 19:28.420
I'm fine.

19:30.700 --> 19:31.900
I just got up too fast.

19:32.430 --> 19:33.530
My head is a little dizzy.

19:33.530 --> 19:34.390
Be careful.

19:34.420 --> 19:35.550
I'm fine. It's okay.

19:36.180 --> 19:36.980
Well...

19:38.740 --> 19:41.350
Then you're not going to
cheer me up anymore?

19:42.290 --> 19:43.170
I've done enough cheering.

19:43.170 --> 19:44.230
What if I get angry?

19:44.230 --> 19:45.960
How are you going to cheer me up?

19:46.970 --> 19:48.990
Honey Liangliang,

19:49.030 --> 19:50.710
you are the best.

19:55.250 --> 19:56.550
Isn't this making me going to heaven?

19:56.550 --> 19:58.560
A Beijing boy can't stand this.

19:58.750 --> 20:00.150
Go sit on the windowsill.

20:00.720 --> 20:01.790
I'll do a flip for you.

20:01.790 --> 20:02.610
Yay!

20:02.640 --> 20:04.000
It's not a kip-up anymore,

20:04.000 --> 20:04.880
it's a flip.

20:04.880 --> 20:05.550
Watch.

20:05.750 --> 20:07.100
1, 2, 3.

20:10.510 --> 20:11.200
How was it?

20:11.680 --> 20:12.550
Another one.

20:13.720 --> 20:14.710
Backflip.

20:18.090 --> 20:18.610
This...

20:20.380 --> 20:21.420
Your hair is all messy.

20:21.420 --> 20:21.770
Well...

20:21.770 --> 20:22.960
I just got up too fast.

20:22.960 --> 20:24.400
My head is just a little dizzy.

20:24.400 --> 20:26.810
This act is over.

20:26.810 --> 20:27.810
There is one more,

20:28.380 --> 20:29.370
a bonus act.

20:31.000 --> 20:31.850
Do you want to see it?

20:31.850 --> 20:32.580
Or maybe not.

20:32.720 --> 20:34.080
No, I want to see it.

20:34.110 --> 20:34.520
Okay.

20:34.550 --> 20:36.880
The next is a disappearing act.

20:42.030 --> 20:42.610
What are you doing?

20:42.610 --> 20:44.340
Why did you take off your socks?

20:44.510 --> 20:45.700
What are you doing?

20:46.920 --> 20:48.070
It hurts.

20:48.680 --> 20:49.940
Look, it hurts me.

20:51.900 --> 20:53.240
Zhuang Zhuang, hurry up.

20:53.240 --> 20:55.720
This is your favorite flatfish.

20:55.740 --> 20:56.090
Look.

20:56.980 --> 20:57.440
Okay.

20:58.010 --> 21:01.140
-Have a taste.
-Your uncle made this especially for you.

21:01.240 --> 21:02.050
It's delicious.

21:02.050 --> 21:02.990
Is it?

21:03.090 --> 21:04.030
It's as yummy as always.

21:04.030 --> 21:04.500
Is it?

21:04.520 --> 21:05.520
Thank you, Uncle.

21:05.530 --> 21:06.530
I don't know if you've gotten used to

21:06.530 --> 21:08.290
staying here these past few days.

21:08.290 --> 21:08.770
It can still get a bit cold

21:08.770 --> 21:10.090
around here in the winter.

21:10.090 --> 21:11.370
If you feel cold, let me know,

21:11.370 --> 21:12.850
and I'll get you another blanket.

21:12.850 --> 21:14.920
No need, it's just fine right now.

21:15.180 --> 21:16.130
I like it here.

21:16.160 --> 21:17.810
It's warm in winter and cool in summer.

21:17.810 --> 21:18.610
Is it?

21:20.680 --> 21:21.410
Have a drink?

21:21.790 --> 21:22.490
Sure.

21:22.570 --> 21:24.700
I'll drink with you even if it kills me.

21:24.740 --> 21:25.270
It's good, huh?

21:25.270 --> 21:27.130
-Come on!
-Eat more if you like it.

21:28.750 --> 21:29.680
You can't outdrink your dad.

21:29.680 --> 21:30.180
I'm telling you.

21:30.180 --> 21:31.530
I have to drink even if
I can't outdrink him.

21:31.530 --> 21:32.110
What do you think?

21:32.110 --> 21:33.790
I bet he drinks a lot when he's out.

21:33.790 --> 21:34.650
Zhuang Zhuang,

21:34.940 --> 21:37.170
you need to keep an eye
on his drinking from now on.

21:37.170 --> 21:37.960
Definitely.

21:38.270 --> 21:39.100
Definitely.

21:39.160 --> 21:40.620
She can drink more than me.

21:41.390 --> 21:42.170
Really?

21:42.260 --> 21:43.220
-Don’t listen to him.
-Just kidding.

21:43.220 --> 21:44.050
Just kidding.

21:44.070 --> 21:44.480
Come on.

21:44.480 --> 21:46.530
We're gathered together again.

21:52.550 --> 21:53.350
Take it easy.

21:53.590 --> 21:54.420
It's a bit cold.

21:54.420 --> 21:55.420
It's fine, right?

21:55.920 --> 21:56.750
I'll do it.

21:56.830 --> 21:57.920
Eat up.

21:58.400 --> 21:58.930
Dad, Mom,

21:59.110 --> 22:00.680
while we're here these couple of days,

22:00.680 --> 22:02.610
we'll take you to see the new house.

22:02.810 --> 22:03.270
So you can

22:03.270 --> 22:04.870
get familiar with the place.

22:08.960 --> 22:09.800
Son,

22:10.460 --> 22:12.460
I think this house is pretty good.

22:12.500 --> 22:14.160
This old house is very comfortable
to live in.

22:14.160 --> 22:14.500
Yeah.

22:14.500 --> 22:15.900
No need to go to all that trouble.

22:15.900 --> 22:18.760
Yeah, it's comfortable
when there're just you two.

22:18.980 --> 22:20.180
But when we come back,

22:20.330 --> 22:21.640
it gets cramped, doesn't it?

22:21.640 --> 22:22.990
Look, when we eat,

22:23.220 --> 22:24.140
we have to move the sofa

22:24.140 --> 22:25.040
and the table.

22:25.070 --> 22:26.270
It's too much hassle.

22:26.660 --> 22:27.840
And not to mention,

22:28.050 --> 22:29.360
in a few years, if we

22:29.680 --> 22:30.700
bring a kid back,

22:31.140 --> 22:32.200
where will we stay?

22:32.530 --> 22:33.860
In the hallway outside?

22:37.220 --> 22:37.880
He's right.

22:37.900 --> 22:38.780
Uncle, Auntie,

22:38.900 --> 22:40.160
that house is by the sea

22:40.310 --> 22:41.440
and it's really big.

22:41.720 --> 22:42.480
If you two move there,

22:42.480 --> 22:44.030
I think it'll be more comfortable.

22:44.030 --> 22:46.380
Look how filial she is.

22:46.480 --> 22:48.020
Um, okay.

22:48.110 --> 22:49.010
Then in the next couple of days,

22:49.010 --> 22:50.000
your uncle and I,

22:50.090 --> 22:51.160
we'll find some time to will go with you

22:51.160 --> 22:52.330
to take a look at the house.

22:52.330 --> 22:52.900
Okay.

22:53.050 --> 22:53.510
Okay.

22:53.880 --> 22:54.630
Okay.

22:54.810 --> 22:55.810
Return the goods?

22:56.880 --> 22:58.880
The factory is already making them.

22:59.050 --> 23:00.010
With such a large volume,

23:00.010 --> 23:01.440
you can't just return them.

23:01.440 --> 23:02.370
What did you say?

23:03.310 --> 23:04.200
Watching TV?

23:04.480 --> 23:05.870
Okay, fine.

23:10.480 --> 23:12.330
According to our correspondent in Moscow,

23:10.990 --> 23:15.310
[News Update]

23:12.590 --> 23:13.550
in the Russian market,

23:13.550 --> 23:15.170
some down jackets made in China

23:15.170 --> 23:17.350
have drawn attention due to
filling issues.

23:17.350 --> 23:18.090
The export volume of related products
to Russia

23:18.090 --> 23:19.880
has declined.

23:20.250 --> 23:22.010
On January 30th local time,

23:22.070 --> 23:23.090
Chinese and Russian regulatory authorities

23:22.920 --> 23:23.850
[Beijing MRX Trading Co., Ltd.]

23:23.090 --> 23:25.720
took coordinated action
to strengthen market supervision

23:25.720 --> 23:27.920
to ensure the order of bilateral trade.

23:28.050 --> 23:28.890
Relevant investigations

23:28.890 --> 23:30.930
and handling are underway.

23:31.960 --> 23:33.700
Here is the detailed report.

23:37.880 --> 23:39.440
Dad, Mom,

23:39.590 --> 23:42.100
we might have to leave tomorrow.

23:42.660 --> 23:43.740
Tomorrow?

23:44.720 --> 23:45.160
Well,

23:46.070 --> 23:47.920
you've only been back for two days.

23:47.920 --> 23:48.900
Why the rush?

23:49.500 --> 23:50.350
Your dad and I

23:50.350 --> 23:51.940
bought a lot of good food.

23:52.000 --> 23:52.500
We were thinking about

23:52.500 --> 23:54.850
stewing some pig trotters
for you tomorrow.

23:54.850 --> 23:56.780
Next time. We'll eat them next time.

23:56.780 --> 23:58.220
They have things to do.

23:58.510 --> 23:59.610
Right.

23:59.750 --> 24:00.890
How about this?

24:01.000 --> 24:01.880
I'll cook

24:01.940 --> 24:02.800
whatever I can,

24:02.900 --> 24:03.900
and then

24:03.900 --> 24:05.550
-pack them up together with the seafood
-Okay.

24:05.550 --> 24:06.670
to take with you.

24:06.790 --> 24:08.160
Mom, no need.

24:08.290 --> 24:09.050
With just the two of us,

24:09.050 --> 24:10.440
carrying so many things

24:10.470 --> 24:11.600
is too much trouble.

24:13.590 --> 24:16.060
Okay, whatever is convenient for you.

24:16.810 --> 24:17.960
All right, let's start eating.

24:17.960 --> 24:19.090
Let's eat, okay?

24:19.180 --> 24:21.180
Let's take them. I love eating them.

24:21.310 --> 24:22.970
We'll take everything we can.

24:23.200 --> 24:24.270
We'll take them all back.

24:24.270 --> 24:25.040
Great.

24:25.180 --> 24:27.240
Then I'll pack them for Zhuang Zhuang.

24:27.240 --> 24:28.240
You don't get any.

24:28.700 --> 24:30.510
I misspoke just now.

24:30.900 --> 24:32.900
Let me have a self-punishing drink.

24:34.330 --> 24:36.680
Don't rush to ship that batch
back to China.

24:36.680 --> 24:38.210
Keep them in the warehouse.

24:38.290 --> 24:39.350
Wait for my notice.

24:41.270 --> 24:41.930
That's all.

24:44.350 --> 24:45.470
Call Zhuang Zhuang

24:45.500 --> 24:46.660
and see how the ticket purchase is going.

24:46.660 --> 24:47.810
No need, my mom is there.

24:47.810 --> 24:48.540
Don't worry.

25:12.250 --> 25:12.710
Hello?

25:13.610 --> 25:14.720
How am I supposed to get back now?

25:14.720 --> 25:15.540
Fly back?

25:16.920 --> 25:18.780
I bought the ticket for tomorrow.

25:20.500 --> 25:22.030
I'll go find you. That's it.

25:51.610 --> 25:52.670
Finished calling?

25:53.140 --> 25:53.790
Finished.

25:54.460 --> 25:55.260
It's nothing.

25:55.620 --> 25:56.480
I can handle it.

25:56.660 --> 25:57.390
Don't worry.

26:01.310 --> 26:02.840
When you are away from home,

26:04.220 --> 26:05.550
no matter what happens,

26:07.000 --> 26:08.970
don't always get too anxious.

26:10.770 --> 26:11.500
Understood.

26:12.400 --> 26:12.990
Also,

26:14.350 --> 26:15.950
about you and Zhuang Zhuang,

26:16.370 --> 26:18.720
find some time to talk to her.

26:19.770 --> 26:21.770
See if her family have any requests,

26:21.940 --> 26:22.640
so we can

26:22.660 --> 26:23.930
prepare in advance.

26:24.660 --> 26:25.660
Whenever you need

26:25.680 --> 26:26.350
me and your mother

26:26.350 --> 26:27.240
to meet them,

26:28.460 --> 26:29.240
just tell us.

26:30.740 --> 26:31.850
Don't worry, Dad.

26:32.290 --> 26:33.000
I know what to do.

26:33.000 --> 26:34.060
You know what to do.

26:36.630 --> 26:38.220
When do you plan to have the wedding?

26:38.220 --> 26:39.720
Let me finish this busy period first.

26:39.720 --> 26:41.100
Finish this period?

26:41.660 --> 26:42.740
When will it end?

26:45.160 --> 26:47.250
You two have been together for years.

26:48.740 --> 26:49.590
Hurry up.

26:51.770 --> 26:53.290
It's not my idea.

26:54.030 --> 26:55.560
It's Zhuang Zhuang's idea.

26:56.440 --> 26:57.010
Okay.

26:58.180 --> 26:59.920
Then do as Zhuang Zhuang says,

27:00.180 --> 27:00.660
okay?

27:00.750 --> 27:01.430
Okay.

27:04.290 --> 27:05.100
Son,

27:07.720 --> 27:08.980
you are better than me.

27:09.790 --> 27:10.650
Look at you now,

27:11.330 --> 27:12.610
you own

27:14.050 --> 27:15.780
a factory with over 100 people.

27:16.750 --> 27:17.940
That means,

27:19.010 --> 27:19.770
behind you,

27:22.650 --> 27:24.280
there are over 100 families.

27:26.420 --> 27:28.350
That's hundreds of mouths to feed.

27:30.350 --> 27:32.190
Leading hundreds of people,

27:32.250 --> 27:33.380
you can't slack off.

27:37.140 --> 27:38.340
Your mother and I

27:39.180 --> 27:41.710
grew up in an environment

27:41.810 --> 27:43.070
that was quite simple.

27:43.940 --> 27:45.250
The only people we interacted with

27:45.250 --> 27:47.940
were from this one factory.

27:51.420 --> 27:52.920
We couldn't teach you

27:53.530 --> 27:55.050
more social experience,

27:55.770 --> 27:57.370
let alone how to do business.

27:58.770 --> 28:00.260
It's all on you

28:00.730 --> 28:01.860
to work hard outside

28:02.310 --> 28:03.770
and brave the world alone.

28:07.140 --> 28:07.920
Out there,

28:08.580 --> 28:10.040
when dealing with people,

28:11.110 --> 28:12.160
be more careful.

28:13.330 --> 28:14.930
Don't let people deceive you

28:14.940 --> 28:15.880
or bully you.

28:17.660 --> 28:19.730
Who can bully your son?

28:20.500 --> 28:22.330
That's good then.

28:26.720 --> 28:28.660
By the way, about that script of yours,

28:28.660 --> 28:29.660
are you still working on it?

28:29.660 --> 28:32.020
Yes, just in my spare time.

28:32.850 --> 28:33.440
Good.

28:38.680 --> 28:39.900
They are coming back soon.

28:39.900 --> 28:40.480
Well...

28:41.030 --> 28:42.520
We need to hurry up and cook.

28:42.520 --> 28:43.700
They'll need to eat when they get back.

28:43.700 --> 28:44.250
Okay.

28:44.250 --> 28:45.250
I'll help you out.

28:45.500 --> 28:46.110
Come over.

29:35.970 --> 29:37.860
[Cao Ye Qigong Research Center]

30:04.380 --> 30:04.920
Master Cao,

30:04.920 --> 30:07.260
you paint really well.

30:09.270 --> 30:09.900
It seems

30:11.400 --> 30:12.740
there are still many things

30:12.740 --> 30:13.940
I need to learn from you.

30:13.940 --> 30:15.340
Miss Luo, you flatter me.

30:18.000 --> 30:18.690
Of course,

30:19.610 --> 30:21.070
as long as you are willing,

30:21.180 --> 30:22.180
I would very much like

30:22.180 --> 30:23.710
to exchange ideas with you.

30:24.930 --> 30:26.330
Is the food to your taste?

30:28.380 --> 30:29.830
Then enjoy.

30:45.790 --> 30:47.680
Liang, what are you standing there for?

30:47.680 --> 30:49.210
Come to the kitchen with me.

30:49.460 --> 30:50.190
Coming, Bro.

31:29.660 --> 31:30.390
Liangliang.

31:40.900 --> 31:42.270
Doctor, what exactly

31:43.240 --> 31:44.300
is going on with me?

31:44.380 --> 31:46.040
Please take a good look for me.

31:46.330 --> 31:47.910
And I've been having headaches recently,

31:47.910 --> 31:49.170
and quite frequently.

31:50.140 --> 31:50.950
Right now,

31:51.050 --> 31:52.450
I can basically conclude

31:53.000 --> 31:54.010
that in your brain,

31:54.010 --> 31:55.170
there is a tumor.

31:56.420 --> 31:57.740
All of your symptoms

31:57.960 --> 31:59.290
are caused by this tumor

31:59.400 --> 32:00.860
compressing your nerves.

32:01.550 --> 32:03.290
Moreover, your tumor's

32:03.310 --> 32:04.560
size and location

32:05.330 --> 32:06.530
are very tricky.

32:21.740 --> 32:22.760
Doctor,

32:23.570 --> 32:25.140
tell me the truth.

32:25.880 --> 32:27.280
How long do I have to live?

32:31.070 --> 32:32.870
Based on the current situation,

32:35.140 --> 32:36.200
half a year at most.

32:59.740 --> 33:01.710
[Olive Tree Apartment]

33:00.330 --> 33:01.260
Tao Liangliang.

33:15.130 --> 33:24.360
[Olive Tree Apartment]

33:33.920 --> 33:34.520
I love you.

33:36.100 --> 33:37.980
Thank you for being in my life.

33:39.110 --> 33:40.480
You said it quite well.

33:40.610 --> 33:41.940
Where did you learn French?

33:41.940 --> 33:43.340
You speak it so fluently.

33:49.440 --> 33:50.040
I love you.

33:52.330 --> 33:53.990
Thank you for being in my life.

34:17.780 --> 34:18.610
I love you too.

34:46.170 --> 34:47.840
They used our brand for the exterior,

34:47.840 --> 34:50.300
but it's stuffed with
shoddy cotton inside.

34:50.340 --> 34:52.159
Did our production details

34:52.360 --> 34:53.020
get leaked?

34:57.570 --> 34:58.430
The zipper is different.

34:58.430 --> 34:59.010
Look.

34:59.670 --> 35:00.470
Our zippers

35:00.550 --> 35:01.620
are custom-made

35:01.650 --> 35:02.850
for export to Russia.

35:03.070 --> 35:04.200
Look at this zipper.

35:04.530 --> 35:06.330
You can tell just by touching it.

35:06.670 --> 35:08.340
Only we have this type of zipper.

35:08.340 --> 35:10.400
You can't buy it in bulk on the market.

35:11.230 --> 35:13.520
Indeed, the quality is much worse.

35:14.400 --> 35:15.260
How about this?

35:15.880 --> 35:16.980
Let's first contact

35:16.980 --> 35:18.570
the distributors in Russia.

35:18.570 --> 35:20.380
Tell them about this
anti-counterfeiting measure.

35:20.380 --> 35:21.500
If they spot any fakes,

35:21.500 --> 35:22.710
they should report them promptly.

35:22.710 --> 35:23.470
Also,

35:23.730 --> 35:24.330
should we

35:24.360 --> 35:25.360
go to the factory?

35:25.710 --> 35:27.000
I'm worried something went wrong

35:27.000 --> 35:27.820
on their end.

35:30.320 --> 35:30.900
Okay.

35:31.280 --> 35:32.530
With the work stopped suddenly,

35:32.530 --> 35:33.870
many people are worried

35:33.980 --> 35:35.320
that their previous efforts were in vain.

35:35.320 --> 35:36.280
As you know,

35:36.510 --> 35:38.410
the workers' wages are based on

35:38.460 --> 35:40.520
a basic salary plus piece-rate pay.

35:40.650 --> 35:43.590
It was supposed to be a good thing
where more work means more pay.

35:43.590 --> 35:44.850
With this suspension,

35:45.030 --> 35:46.430
many people have asked me

35:49.650 --> 35:51.450
if they'll eventually get paid.

35:51.980 --> 35:52.860
They are worried.

35:52.860 --> 35:53.570
Ren,

35:53.760 --> 35:55.110
don't worry about that.

35:55.350 --> 35:56.530
You know what kind of

35:56.550 --> 35:57.350
people we are.

35:57.610 --> 35:59.610
We won't short anyone a single cent.

35:59.800 --> 36:00.800
That's good then.

36:01.780 --> 36:03.690
I saw the news report from a few days ago.

36:03.690 --> 36:04.690
About Russia boycotting

36:04.690 --> 36:05.950
Chinese down jackets.

36:06.010 --> 36:06.730
I saw our clothes

36:06.730 --> 36:07.940
on the news.

36:08.210 --> 36:09.540
Our brand label

36:09.560 --> 36:10.960
was prominently displayed.

36:10.960 --> 36:13.300
The clothes were piled up and burned.

36:13.920 --> 36:14.360
I mean,

36:14.380 --> 36:15.780
what exactly is going on?

36:16.420 --> 36:18.030
The situation in Russia

36:18.150 --> 36:19.090
didn't just happen

36:19.090 --> 36:20.010
overnight.

36:20.610 --> 36:21.780
It's been building up for a long time

36:21.780 --> 36:23.440
and just exploded all at once.

36:26.510 --> 36:27.760
They don't make things properly,

36:27.760 --> 36:28.720
and in the end,

36:29.000 --> 36:30.730
it hurts all Chinese goods.

36:30.860 --> 36:32.160
It screwed us over too,

36:32.280 --> 36:32.980
right?

36:33.190 --> 36:35.190
Let's just have a good New Year first

36:35.230 --> 36:36.920
and try to start work again
after the New Year.

36:36.920 --> 36:38.560
Just set your mind at ease,

36:38.620 --> 36:39.690
and help us control the quality.

36:39.690 --> 36:40.350
That'll do.

36:41.900 --> 36:43.160
Okay, don't worry.

37:22.460 --> 37:23.450
You're back.

37:23.760 --> 37:25.220
Hurry up. Wash up and rest.

37:25.320 --> 37:26.540
Okay, honey.

37:27.010 --> 37:28.210
You go ahead and rest.

37:29.310 --> 37:30.300
Honey.

37:31.400 --> 37:32.710
I sold

37:32.740 --> 37:34.080
60 down jackets today.

37:36.090 --> 37:37.250
You are amazing.

37:39.050 --> 37:40.060
Nothing amazing.

37:51.980 --> 37:53.310
Every little bit helps.

38:00.000 --> 38:01.260
How much did you drink?

38:01.960 --> 38:02.880
Not much.

38:04.200 --> 38:04.690
Director Yang

38:04.690 --> 38:05.830
called me today.

38:06.860 --> 38:09.000
He said you withdrew money
from the shoe factory again.

38:09.000 --> 38:10.440
He also said you've been
socializing a lot lately

38:10.440 --> 38:11.310
and asked me to take care of you.

38:11.310 --> 38:12.900
Well, since we are doing business,

38:12.900 --> 38:14.700
socializing is totally normal.

38:14.710 --> 38:15.640
But this Yang,

38:15.670 --> 38:16.390
I told him

38:16.420 --> 38:17.670
not to tell you,

38:18.190 --> 38:19.520
but he still did anyway.

38:20.050 --> 38:22.650
How long were you planning
to keep this from me?

38:35.030 --> 38:35.750
Here.

38:38.460 --> 38:39.520
Careful, it's hot.

38:41.340 --> 38:41.900
Is it hot?

38:45.960 --> 38:47.160
Let me take it myself.

38:56.570 --> 38:58.940
When you said the factory would
resume work,

38:58.940 --> 39:01.400
you were planning
to borrow money yourself?

39:03.320 --> 39:04.580
Why didn't you tell me?

39:07.910 --> 39:08.730
Since now

39:09.780 --> 39:11.090
we haven't found any sales channels yet,

39:11.090 --> 39:12.620
telling you would only

39:13.260 --> 39:14.900
make you worry with me.

39:15.440 --> 39:16.320
So you were going to

39:16.320 --> 39:17.360
bear it all alone?

39:19.510 --> 39:21.170
I can handle it. It's nothing.

39:30.690 --> 39:31.170
Do you remember

39:31.170 --> 39:32.300
when my mom was sick?

39:34.360 --> 39:35.880
I only found out

39:37.150 --> 39:37.780
after Jun told me

39:37.780 --> 39:39.580
that your movie didn't get made.

39:39.670 --> 39:41.470
I was so scared after I found out.

39:41.920 --> 39:42.460
I was scared that

39:42.460 --> 39:43.870
if Jun hadn't told me,

39:44.230 --> 39:46.430
if you hadn't come to Wenzhou to find me,

39:47.830 --> 39:49.110
I might never have known

39:49.110 --> 39:50.530
you had such a hard time.

40:01.840 --> 40:02.970
I also blamed myself

40:05.430 --> 40:07.030
that when you needed me most,

40:08.610 --> 40:09.810
I wasn't by your side.

40:11.530 --> 40:13.480
It's fine. It's fine.

40:17.110 --> 40:18.850
So I decided then

40:20.960 --> 40:23.290
that no matter what happens in the future,

40:24.920 --> 40:26.320
we will face it together.

40:28.130 --> 40:28.970
With you here,

40:30.320 --> 40:31.530
even if we have nothing,

40:31.530 --> 40:32.590
the sky won't fall.

40:41.230 --> 40:42.290
Why are you crying?

40:43.320 --> 40:44.060
I'm happy.

40:46.300 --> 40:46.760
Today, I

40:46.780 --> 40:48.680
looked into the details

40:48.820 --> 40:50.220
of mortgaging the house.

40:50.420 --> 40:51.140
The house

40:51.160 --> 40:52.820
can be mortgaged for 250,000.

40:52.920 --> 40:54.780
I also discussed with the factory

40:55.030 --> 40:57.030
the possibility of reducing costs.

40:57.100 --> 40:58.700
I think from now on, we should

40:59.350 --> 41:01.210
sell retail at wholesale prices.

41:02.150 --> 41:04.150
As long as our price is competitive,

41:04.310 --> 41:06.570
our customers will have better margins.

41:06.900 --> 41:08.430
As long as we keep shipping,

41:08.630 --> 41:09.300
the market will definitely

41:09.300 --> 41:10.560
get better gradually.

41:15.690 --> 41:17.420
But you love this house so much.

41:20.030 --> 41:20.710
All right.

41:22.340 --> 41:23.140
I support you.

41:24.010 --> 41:25.610
It doesn't matter if we make money or not.

41:25.610 --> 41:27.350
We have to win the market back.

41:30.000 --> 41:32.200
We'll fight this long battle together.

41:32.960 --> 41:33.690
Let's fight.

41:35.500 --> 41:37.000
If we win this time...

41:37.030 --> 41:38.090
We'll get married.

41:45.880 --> 41:47.490
What if we lose?

41:47.900 --> 41:49.300
We'll still get married.

42:02.010 --> 42:03.730
There's this popular term these days.

42:03.730 --> 42:04.790
What was it called?

42:05.570 --> 42:06.770
"Beijing drifters."

42:09.530 --> 42:10.730
We are so young.

42:13.230 --> 42:16.160
Worst case, we start over
as Beijing drifters again.

42:17.150 --> 42:17.730
Drift.

42:18.980 --> 42:20.150
We can drift anywhere,

42:20.150 --> 42:21.550
as long as you are with me.

42:27.000 --> 42:28.430
I've also figured it out.

42:30.140 --> 42:32.640
Whether the house is rented

42:32.670 --> 42:33.640
or bought.

42:35.010 --> 42:38.000
whether we're poor or rich,

42:39.070 --> 42:41.210
our life together is our own.

42:42.570 --> 42:44.970
I have the determination
to make you happy.

42:49.690 --> 42:50.320
Why are you suddenly

42:50.320 --> 42:51.710
saying wedding vows?

42:52.730 --> 42:54.710
I've always wanted to marry you.
